sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Caller
    participant G as AXME Cloud Gateway
    participant I as Identity Validator
    participant Z as Authorization Engine
    participant A as Audit/Trace

    C->>G: API request
    G->>I: validate x-api-key
    alt api key invalid
        I-->>G: invalid
        G-->>C: 401
    else api key valid
        I-->>G: ok
        G->>I: validate bearer (if required)
        alt bearer invalid/scope mismatch
            I-->>G: reject
            G-->>C: 401/403
        else identity valid
            G->>Z: enforce owner scope + role/grants
            alt unauthorized
                Z-->>G: deny
                G-->>C: 403
            else authorized
                Z-->>G: allow
                G->>A: record audit + trace metadata
                G-->>C: execute and return response
            end
        end
    end
